would encourage you to check with his advisors to get them to explain to yo=
u what it means to &#8220;eliminate ISIS.&#8221;&nbsp; Or at least what he =
means when he says that.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Before =
