<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Well, I'=
d refer you to HHS and they can give you some more details on exactly what =
those studies and what those tests have found.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; There also has been work to=
 provide additional assistance -- economic assistance to Flint.&nbsp; The c=
