t of a natural disaster, and this disaster is obviously a man-made one.<o:p=
></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; So th=
ere will be a federal disaster -- declaring it a federal disaster area, ess=
entially.<o:p></o:p></p>
