y.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We've=
 had more calls and discussions with residents out there, and the feeling i=
s -- and as we've talked about before -- there's a huge trust deficit now -=
-<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; Sure.<=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -- th=
at may not be reparable given what's happened for some certainly.&nbsp; Is =
there some contemplation by the administration of trying to find some other=
 way to broaden the federal role there going forward?&nbsp; If,
