<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">MR. EARNEST:&nbsp; At thi=
s point, Andrew, I'm not aware of a change in our position.&nbsp; Obviously=
 we'll keep you posted if something like that is being contemplated in adva=
nce of the trip.&nbsp; I anticipate that the President,
 when he travels to Vietnam, will actually spend most of his time talking a=
